Right click on Desktop to access the menu!

PLEASE remember:
- to change autostart application, openbox menu, keyboard layout and locales: right-click on desktop and go to
  Configurations submenu. Step by step all configuration will be migrated to Administrator mode.
- to add Desktop icon just add a .desktop file in $HOME/Desktop/ like the others
- to enable monitor sleep mode remove the file $HOME/.xsessionrc
- Dual Kernel: just change config.txt and change the line: kernel=kernel.img in kernel=kernel-std.img

NEW Feature:
- Administrator Mode: press K (shift+k) during boot video intro to enter root mode. Password is "LOL"
- Browser Mode: press B (shift+b) diring boot video intro to enter browser only mode.